 to reconcile their hopes and expectations for a Promised Land with the realities of life on the early American frontier.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 0aChristianity and geographyzOhiozWestern ReservexHistoryy19th century. 0aCongregational churchesxMissionszConnecticutzOhiozWestern ReservexHistoryy19th century. 0aMissionszOhiozWestern ReservexHistoryy19th century. 0aPresbyterian ChurchxMissionszOhiozWestern ReservexHistoryy19th century. 7aRELIGION / Religion, Politics & State.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCUP eBook Package 2000-2015z978311066254208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311044247208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014z978311045952440uhttps://doi.org/10.7312/dero12788423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780231508599.jpg  a978-3-11-044247-2  CUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013  a978-3-11-045952-4  CUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014c2000d2014  a978-3-11-066254-2  CUP eBook Package 2000-2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG